 <title>How AllJoyn Makes A Better Product</title>
 <link>https://identity.allseenalliance.org/news/blogs/2015/03/how-alljoyn-makes-better-product</link>
 <description>
		&lt;span class=&quot;a2a_kit a2a_target addtoany_list&quot; id=&quot;da2a_1&quot;&gt;
